
- MySQL Show the schema of a table

Usage:
describe [db_name.]table_name;
SHOW create table [db_name.]table_name;
SHOW columns from [db_name.]table_name;


- MySQL LIKE syntax

Usage:
SELECT * FROM table WHERE column [NOT] LIKE pattern; //精準匹配
SELECT * FROM table WHERE column [NOT] LIKE %pattern%; //類似匹配
SELECT * FROM table WHERE column [NOT] LIKE BINARY pattern; //區分大小寫
